Entry.JapaneseText: オレは<Veigue>・リュングベルだ。
フォルス……オレとクレア、そして カレギアの運命を変えたこの力……
Entry.EnglishText: Force... That's the power that has changed the fate of myself and Claire, as well as that of Callegea...

Entry.JapaneseText: 乗り越えてみせる……必ず……
Entry.EnglishText: I am going to get through this... I'm sure of it...
